<p>Her husband Prince Albert look as equally as sophisticated in a white shirt, black suit and matching bow-tie.</p>

<p>The couple, who appeared to be in deep conversation during their red carpet appearance, also posed with English singer Sting.</p>

<p>The 2020 Monte-Carlo Gala for Planetary Health aims to highlight the idea that our future is dependent on healthy ecosystems.</p>

